### Issues Found (non-blocking)
1. **Credential mismatch in deploy.out**: deploy.out stated `admin@orschell.com / admin123`; actual credentials (shown on login page and in DB) are `admin@orschellsupply.com / Admin1234!`. All flows work with correct credentials.
2. **`GET /api/products/categories`** conflicts with product-by-slug route (returns 404). Correct endpoint is `/api/categories`. Frontend uses the correct endpoint; no user-facing impact.
3. **Stray test products** (CEO Test Widget, Deploy Test Product, Test Product) at 0 stock in inventory from QA runs; cosmetic only.

