## Summary

All hero flows verified live with Playwright against deployed demo and API bridge.
- Customer: browse 26 products, add-to-cart (drawer with subtotal), checkout (mock payment, MOCK- ref), order history
- Admin: dashboard (revenue chart, KPIs), product catalog management, order pipeline (status updates persist), inventory tracking
- Auth: login, registration, role-based access (403 on admin routes with customer token)
- No console errors; /work-samples route loads; all stated e-commerce features exercised

## handoff
- produced: full Playwright live test; all stated flows pass; credential correction documented
- decisions: work-samples SPA 404 is expected GH Pages behavior (not a failure); order status update route is PUT /api/admin/orders/:id/status; cart uses product_id (snake_case) not productId
- next needs: media-capture — screenshot /#/shop (hero) and /#/admin (dashboard); use admin@orschellsupply.com / Admin1234! for admin panel capture
- risks: test order/product noise in DB (cosmetic); stale orders #3-#5 visible in admin orders list

